Object Parameters:
0 = Green Shell
1 = Red Shell
2 = Banana
3 = Mushroom
4 = Star
Description:
Object used in tournaments (Daisy Circuit and SNES Battle Course 4).
Can be used to place an item directly onto the track; they will not show up in Time Trials.
You must not place more than 11 of these in a track; otherwise, your track will freeze or hang in online play.
